Sentencas: Mn and Fe co-doped CeO2-delta (denoted as CMF) film was prepared with pulsed laser deposition (PLD) method and the obtained CMF dense film was studied as anode for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Ce(Mn,Fe)O2 dense film deposited on LaGaO3 electrolyte for dense anode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The deposited CMF film showed much higher electrical conductivity than that of CMF disk in various oxygen partial pressures.
Titulo: Ce(Mn,Fe)O2 dense film deposited on LaGaO3 electrolyte for dense anode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, the CMF thin film improved power density of LSGM-supported solid oxide fuel cell with decreasing internal resistance.
Titulo: Ce(Mn,Fe)O2 dense film deposited on LaGaO3 electrolyte for dense anode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cell using bi-layer anode, which was consisted of thin film and powder-CMF, exhibited 3 times larger power density than that of the cell using only CMF powder anode.
Titulo: Ce(Mn,Fe)O2 dense film deposited on LaGaO3 electrolyte for dense anode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, the cell using only CMF thin film anode showed fairly large power density (131 mW/cm(2)) despite of narrow active surface area.
Titulo: Ce(Mn,Fe)O2 dense film deposited on LaGaO3 electrolyte for dense anode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Therefore, the bi-layer anode consisted of thin and dense CMF film and porous powder is active anode for solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Ce(Mn,Fe)O2 dense film deposited on LaGaO3 electrolyte for dense anode of solid oxide fuel cells
